```

---

## ğŸ“· Visual Example

Use NetworkX + PyTorch Geometric to visualize the graph:

```python
import torch
import networkx as nx
from torch_geometric.utils import to_networkx

graph = torch.load("demo_graph.pt")
G = to_networkx(graph)
nx.draw(G, with_labels=True)
```

